name: I've Got A Bad Feeling About This
Lore: 'Han''s smuggling adventures in Corporate Sector and Hutt Space put him in many tight scrapes. He''s about to be in another.',
Text: 'If you just initiated a battle at a location where you have less power than the opponent, double opponent''s battle damage if you win the battle (if Han is present at the battle location, triple opponent''s battle damage).',
